                                </mrow>
                              </annotation-xml>
                            </semantics>
                          </math> The least probable configuration of the system is one in which all four particles are in one box, corresponding to distributions (a) and (e), each with a probability of
                          <math display="inline">
                            <semantics>
                              <mrow>
                                <mrow>
                                  <mfrac>
                                    <mn>1</mn>
                                    <mrow>
