                          <p id="fs-idm200549408">
                            <span data-type="title">Solution</span>
                            (a) positive, temperature increases
                          </p>
                          <p
                            id="fs-idm136327104"
                          >(b) negative, reduction in the number of ions (particles) in solution, decreased dispersal of matter</p>
                          <p
                            id="fs-idm137858960"
                          >(c) negative, net decrease in the amount of gaseous species</p>
                          <p
                            id="fs-idm119107312"
                          >(d) positive, phase transition from solid to liquid, net increase in dispersal of matter</p>
                          <p id="fs-idm10344720">
