                          <div data-type="note" id="fs-idm8656368">
                            <h3 class="os-title" data-type="title">
                              <span
                                class="os-title-label"
                                data-type
                                id="[redacted for uniqueness]"
                              >Answer:</span>
                            </h3>
                            <div class="os-note-body">
                              <p
                                id="fs-idm140480768"
                              >(a) Positive; The solid dissolves to give an increase of mobile ions in solution. (b) Negative; The liquid becomes a more ordered solid. (c) Positive; The relatively ordered solid becomes a gas. (d) Positive; There is a net increase in the amount of gaseous species.</p>
                            </div>
